@node Key-Bindings
@section Summary of Key-Bindings

All default org-trello key-bindings use the “C-c o” prefix.

@table @asis
@item C-c o v
Display the version of org-trello.
@end table

@node Synchronization Functions
@section Synchronization Functions

This section describes the synchronization functions.
@vtable @code
@item org-trello-sync-buffer
Use “C-c o s” to sync the entire buffer to the Trello board.@*
Use “C-u C-c o s” to sync the entire buffer from the Trello board.
@end vtable
@findex org-trello-sync-buffer
@kindex C-c o s

